(2040, 1, '2018-02-01 11:39:44', '2018-02-01 19:39:44', 'This was a group project where we had to design a single webpage. I had the position of Designer and the following images show all of my work step by step.\r\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\">Wireframe</h5>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2042\" src=\"http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/pm_team1_wireframes-1024x770.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"625\" height=\"470\" />\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\">First Rough\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2043\" src=\"http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Craig-First-rough-339x1024.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"339\" height=\"1024\" /></h5>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\">Second Rough<img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-2044\" src=\"http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Craig-Second-rough-315x1024.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"315\" height=\"1024\" /></h5>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Craig-Final-Rough-Comp.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Craig Final Rough Comp</a></h4>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Final_site_design_3-2.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">FINAL Complete Site Design</a></h3>', 'IMG-130: Project Management', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'img-130-project-management', '', '', '2018-03-08 15:54:14', '2018-03-08 23:54:14', '', 0, 'http://localhost/?p=2040', 0, 'post', '', 0),
